# Link Installation

You can [install Paper package](https://www.nuget.org/packages/Skclusive.Material.Component/) by typing the below command in your terminal:

```csharp
dotnet add package Skclusive.Material.Component
```

Then, you can import it in your `_Imports.razor`.

```csharp
@using Skclusive.Material.Component
```

Then, you can render the style for this component it in your `Router.razor`.

```html
<LinkStyle />
```

